      "role": "user",
      "content": "it’s just so heavy lately. like, i look at everything and there’s just nothing. no purpose, no cosmic plan, just atoms bumping into each other until they stop. it feels like i'm just waiting for the inevitable and there's no point in fighting the weight of it all.",
