    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but even those small moments feel forced. like, why bother building a tiny world just to watch it crumble eventually? it's just delaying the only thing that's actually certain. the end. everything just ends anyway, so why keep dragging this around.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
